quran[11]{c,v,t}:
  62,1,Yesebbihu lillahi ma fiyssemavati ve ma fiylÂṀardÄḟl elmelikilkuddusil-ÂṀaziyzilhakiymi
  62,2,Huvelleziy beÂṀase fiylÂṀummiyyiyne resulen minhum yetlu ÂṀaleyhim ayatihi ve yuzekkiyhim ve yuÂṀallimuhumulkitabe velhÄḟkmete ve inkanu min kablu lefiy dalalin mubiynin
  62,3,Ve ahariyne minhum lemma yelhaku bihim ve huvelÂṀaziyzulhakiymu
  62,4,Zalike fadlullahi yuÂṀtiyhi men yeÅaÂṀu vallahu zulfadlilÂṀazÄḟymi
  62,5,Meselulleziyne hummiluttevrate summe lem yahmiluha kemeselilhÄḟmari yahmilu esfaren biÂṀse meselulkavmilleziyne kezzebu biayatillahi vallahu la yehdiylkavmezzalimiyne
  62,6,Kul ya eyyuhelleziyne hadu in zeÂṀamtum ennekum evliyau lillahi min duninnasi fetemennevulmevte in kuntum sadikÄḟyne
  62,7,Ve la yetemennevnehu ebeden bima kaddemet eydiyhim vallahu ÂṀaliymun bizzalimiyne
  62,8,Kul innelmevtelleziy tefirrune minhu feinnehu mulakÄḟykum summe tureddune ila ÂṀalimilÄaybi veÅÅehadeti feyunebiiukum bima kuntum taÂṀmelune
  62,9,Ya eyyuhelleziyne amenu iza nudiye lissalati min yevmilcumuÂṀati fesÂṀav ila zikrillahi ve zerulbeyÂṀa zalikum hayrun lekum in kuntum taÂṀlemune
  62,10,Feiza kudÄḟyetissalatu fenteÅiru fiylÂṀardÄḟ vebteÄu min fadlillahi vezkurullahe kesiyren leÂṀallekum tuflihune
  62,11,Ve iza reev ticareten ev lehveninfaddu ileyha ve terekuke kaimen kul ma ÂṀÄḟndallahi hayrun millehvi ve minetticareti vallahu hayrurrazikÄḟyne